1
00:01:33,360 --> 00:01:34,950
[OVERDO]

2
00:01:35,340 --> 00:01:37,680
[Episode 6]

3
00:01:40,660 --> 00:01:43,210
[Spirit tablet of
the late respected father, Murong Feng]

4
00:01:41,400 --> 00:01:42,430
Rebellious son!

5
00:01:43,430 --> 00:01:44,229
Kneel!

6
00:01:46,759 --> 00:01:48,690
Bringing those despicable things

7
00:01:48,710 --> 00:01:50,770
into the ancestral hall is unfilial!

8
00:01:51,280 --> 00:01:53,640
How did I give birth to such a bastard?

9
00:01:54,640 --> 00:01:56,200
Even Huo Minxian knows

10
00:01:56,710 --> 00:01:58,870
that you can't have a son,
neglect to raise him,

11
00:01:58,870 --> 00:02:00,840
and then expect him to turn out perfect.

12
00:02:00,840 --> 00:02:02,570
Get your head out of the clouds.

13
00:02:03,710 --> 00:02:04,400
You...

14
00:02:35,960 --> 00:02:36,560
Mother.

15
00:02:37,120 --> 00:02:38,590
Mulan needs to go to the hospital.

16
00:02:38,590 --> 00:02:39,650
We'll leave first.

17
00:02:39,710 --> 00:02:40,430
Go now.

18
00:03:25,230 --> 00:03:28,740
[Murong Residence]

19
00:03:28,840 --> 00:03:31,000
You defended Qingyi so strongly today.

20
00:03:31,000 --> 00:03:32,800
But you're not even close to him.

21
00:03:34,750 --> 00:03:36,150
I can feel that

22
00:03:36,360 --> 00:03:37,690
you care about him a lot.

23
00:03:39,520 --> 00:03:41,079
But in front of your mother,

24
00:03:41,750 --> 00:03:43,400
you are always in a dilemma.

25
00:03:44,310 --> 00:03:45,710
You want to protect him,

26
00:03:46,000 --> 00:03:47,600
yet you have to consider her.

27
00:03:50,079 --> 00:03:51,520
And I can feel

28
00:03:52,120 --> 00:03:53,800
that he cares about you too.

29
00:03:54,750 --> 00:03:56,870
Since you two are so close as brothers,

30
00:03:56,870 --> 00:03:58,280
as his sister-in-law,

31
00:03:58,280 --> 00:03:59,480
I should help him out.

32
00:04:03,280 --> 00:04:05,210
Thank you for being so thoughtful.

33
00:04:06,470 --> 00:04:07,730
Actually, 3 years ago,

34
00:04:08,080 --> 00:04:09,190
he was wronged.

35
00:04:10,680 --> 00:04:12,000
At that time,

36
00:04:12,520 --> 00:04:14,250
I really couldn't protect him.

37
00:04:14,430 --> 00:04:16,310
I could only trade 3 years of his freedom

38
00:04:16,310 --> 00:04:18,360
for the Huo family to spare his life.

39
00:04:19,680 --> 00:04:20,680
Since then,

40
00:04:21,600 --> 00:04:23,130
he has been distant from me.

41
00:04:30,830 --> 00:04:32,490
Perhaps he suffered even more

42
00:04:34,360 --> 00:04:35,680
than you have seen.

43
00:04:40,560 --> 00:04:41,360
Come in.

44
00:04:46,510 --> 00:04:47,710
What brings you here?

45
00:04:49,920 --> 00:04:51,320
Sister-in-law saved me.

46
00:04:51,720 --> 00:04:52,920
I'm here to thank her.

47
00:05:08,680 --> 00:05:09,560
So say it.

48
00:05:12,000 --> 00:05:13,120
I only want to thank

49
00:05:14,040 --> 00:05:15,070
Sister-in-law.

50
00:05:29,000 --> 00:05:29,680
Alright.

51
00:05:30,390 --> 00:05:31,450
I'll go rest first.

52
00:05:31,870 --> 00:05:33,200
Don't talk for too long.

53
00:05:49,310 --> 00:05:50,000
Eat up.

54
00:05:50,630 --> 00:05:53,230
It will wash away
the bitterness in your mouth.

55
00:05:56,040 --> 00:05:58,900
I like eating candied fruit
after taking medicine.

56
00:05:59,240 --> 00:05:59,830
Really?

57
00:06:00,830 --> 00:06:01,920
But you used to

58
00:06:02,270 --> 00:06:04,400
always leave the candied fruit for me.

59
00:06:08,560 --> 00:06:09,800
The past is the past.

60
00:06:13,310 --> 00:06:14,720
The past is the past?

61
00:06:21,310 --> 00:06:22,430
In the past,

62
00:06:22,680 --> 00:06:24,680
you left all the sweet things for me.

63
00:06:24,720 --> 00:06:25,390
From now on,

64
00:06:26,600 --> 00:06:28,060
I will give them all to you.

65
00:07:08,560 --> 00:07:09,430
Help!

66
00:07:09,430 --> 00:07:10,310
You can't bear to see it?

67
00:07:10,310 --> 00:07:11,190
Help!

68
00:07:11,600 --> 00:07:12,480
Help!

69
00:07:13,120 --> 00:07:15,480
But who ever showed us
any mercy back then?

70
00:07:16,040 --> 00:07:18,000
Don't forget what we went through

71
00:07:18,190 --> 00:07:19,430
and where we came from.

72
00:07:19,430 --> 00:07:22,000
Every breath we take now

73
00:07:22,240 --> 00:07:24,100
is borrowed from the King of Hell.

74
00:07:24,390 --> 00:07:25,950
I'll kill you!

75
00:07:25,950 --> 00:07:27,240
What we need to do

76
00:07:28,000 --> 00:07:29,750
must never be abandoned

77
00:07:30,160 --> 00:07:31,510
due to a moment of pity.

78
00:07:37,000 --> 00:07:38,900
[Murong Residence]

79
00:08:00,000 --> 00:08:00,920
With me here,

80
00:08:01,040 --> 00:08:02,000
don't be afraid.

81
00:08:03,040 --> 00:08:05,160
I like eating candied fruit
after taking medicine.

82
00:08:05,160 --> 00:08:06,070
In the past,

83
00:08:06,720 --> 00:08:08,720
you left all the sweet things for me.

84
00:08:08,800 --> 00:08:10,930
From now on, I will give them all to you.

85
00:08:22,480 --> 00:08:23,560
Young Master Qingyi.

86
00:08:23,560 --> 00:08:24,310
Bad news.

87
00:08:24,800 --> 00:08:26,130
Huo Minxian is missing.

88
00:08:33,000 --> 00:08:33,840
Zongqi,

89
00:08:34,150 --> 00:08:35,510
I know we, a widow and her daughter,

90
00:08:35,510 --> 00:08:37,039
are living under your roof.

91
00:08:38,200 --> 00:08:39,120
But Minxian

92
00:08:39,360 --> 00:08:41,360
is your cousin after all.

93
00:08:41,360 --> 00:08:43,200
You can't just ignore
whether she's dead or alive.

94
00:08:43,200 --> 00:08:44,330
Then you go find her.

95
00:08:44,480 --> 00:08:45,790
But where is she?

96
00:08:45,790 --> 00:08:46,630
Aunt,

97
00:08:47,270 --> 00:08:48,750
I have already sent people
to look for her.

98
00:08:48,750 --> 00:08:50,360
You have to wait for the news.

99
00:08:50,360 --> 00:08:52,510
We shouldn't panic now, should we?

100
00:08:55,120 --> 00:08:56,320
Madam, Young Master.

101
00:08:56,670 --> 00:08:57,670
Someone told me

102
00:08:57,670 --> 00:08:59,270
they saw Her Ladyship heading west.

103
00:08:59,270 --> 00:09:00,270
I followed that direction

104
00:09:00,270 --> 00:09:02,600
and found this on the riverbank in Luzhou.

105
00:09:07,080 --> 00:09:07,680
This is...

106
00:09:08,360 --> 00:09:09,870
This is the shoe Minxian was wearing

107
00:09:09,870 --> 00:09:10,550
when she went out

108
00:09:10,550 --> 00:09:12,270
on the day she disappeared.

109
00:09:12,960 --> 00:09:14,080
Minxian...

110
00:09:14,910 --> 00:09:15,670
Minxian!

111
00:09:17,750 --> 00:09:19,600
She just went to the Murong family's
ancestral hall.

112
00:09:19,600 --> 00:09:20,600
How could this...

113
00:09:25,750 --> 00:09:27,440
Murong Qingyi.

114
00:09:28,910 --> 00:09:29,600
What?

115
00:09:29,750 --> 00:09:31,080
Huo Minxian is missing?

116
00:09:31,510 --> 00:09:32,030
Yes.

117
00:09:33,630 --> 00:09:35,030
After she came out
of the ancestral hall yesterday,

118
00:09:35,030 --> 00:09:36,720
she didn't return to the Huo family.

119
00:09:36,720 --> 00:09:38,030
Later, by the river,

120
00:09:38,150 --> 00:09:40,150
remnants of her clothes were found.

121
00:09:40,270 --> 00:09:42,530
The salvage team hasn't found a body yet.

122
00:09:42,750 --> 00:09:43,440
Her fate...

123
00:09:44,200 --> 00:09:45,120
is unknown.

124
00:09:53,510 --> 00:09:55,510
I happen to be in charge of this case.

125
00:09:56,030 --> 00:09:57,150
The Huo family said

126
00:09:57,840 --> 00:09:59,790
if something really happened to her,

127
00:09:59,790 --> 00:10:01,600
they will not only
break off the engagement,

128
00:10:01,600 --> 00:10:02,390
but also...

129
00:10:03,240 --> 00:10:04,500
sue our Murong family.

130
00:10:08,360 --> 00:10:09,560
It must have been you!

131
00:10:10,200 --> 00:10:12,270
You caused more trouble for the family.

132
00:10:12,270 --> 00:10:13,930
Where exactly is Huo Minxian?

133
00:10:14,360 --> 00:10:15,910
How would I know where she is?

134
00:10:15,910 --> 00:10:17,030
How would you know?

135
00:10:17,320 --> 00:10:18,120
Yesterday...

136
00:10:18,550 --> 00:10:21,270
Yesterday,
what did you say in the ancestral hall?

137
00:10:21,270 --> 00:10:23,200
You said you wanted to make her disappear.

138
00:10:23,200 --> 00:10:24,330
What a coincidence.

139
00:10:24,630 --> 00:10:26,120
She really disappeared.

140
00:10:28,790 --> 00:10:29,790
Tell us the truth.

141
00:10:30,600 --> 00:10:31,330
Where is she?

142
00:10:31,670 --> 00:10:32,840
Is she alive or dead?

143
00:10:33,270 --> 00:10:34,630
Didn't I tell you?

144
00:10:34,720 --> 00:10:35,320
It wasn't me.

145
00:10:35,320 --> 00:10:36,720
I don't know where she is.

146
00:10:39,360 --> 00:10:40,240
If it wasn't you,

147
00:10:40,240 --> 00:10:41,080
then who else?

148
00:10:41,080 --> 00:10:42,210
Who else could it be?

149
00:10:43,320 --> 00:10:44,600
Who else could it be?

150
00:10:45,000 --> 00:10:46,510
My late father, of course!

151
00:10:47,000 --> 00:10:48,840
He's trying to crawl out of the ground

152
00:10:48,840 --> 00:10:51,030
and take away his stupid daughter-in-law!

153
00:10:51,030 --> 00:10:51,480
You...

154
00:10:52,080 --> 00:10:52,670
Mother!

155
00:10:52,870 --> 00:10:53,360
Mother!

156
00:10:53,630 --> 00:10:54,240
Mother!

157
00:10:54,440 --> 00:10:55,040
Calm down!

158
00:10:55,390 --> 00:10:56,850
Qingyi said it wasn't him!

159
00:10:58,030 --> 00:10:58,870
Yesterday,

160
00:10:59,080 --> 00:11:00,340
in the ancestral hall,

161
00:11:00,440 --> 00:11:02,030
he threatened Huo Minxian in public.

162
00:11:02,030 --> 00:11:03,510
Everyone heard it.

163
00:11:03,910 --> 00:11:05,790
He also abducted
the people Huo Minxian brought.

164
00:11:05,790 --> 00:11:07,190
Now you say it wasn't you?

165
00:11:07,270 --> 00:11:08,600
Who would believe that?

166
00:11:08,600 --> 00:11:09,270
I think

167
00:11:09,270 --> 00:11:11,120
you're nothing
but the reincarnation of a jinx.

168
00:11:11,120 --> 00:11:11,790
How could you do things

169
00:11:11,790 --> 00:11:13,990
without considering our family at all?

170
00:11:14,750 --> 00:11:15,510
Now,

171
00:11:15,720 --> 00:11:17,510
not only have we failed to form
a marriage alliance with the Huo family,

172
00:11:17,510 --> 00:11:19,360
but we've also made enemies of them.

173
00:11:19,360 --> 00:11:20,000
Oh no.

174
00:11:20,360 --> 00:11:22,490
The planes are out of the question too.

175
00:11:23,390 --> 00:11:24,510
I believe Qingyi.

176
00:11:25,630 --> 00:11:26,440
If, because of

177
00:11:26,720 --> 00:11:28,120
Qingyi's impulsive words yesterday,

178
00:11:28,120 --> 00:11:29,600
Huo Minxian happened to disappear,

179
00:11:29,600 --> 00:11:31,200
it would be too much of a coincidence.

180
00:11:31,200 --> 00:11:32,470
So there must be someone

181
00:11:32,470 --> 00:11:34,200
pulling the strings behind it.

182
00:11:36,200 --> 00:11:37,530
Where are you going now?

183
00:11:39,440 --> 00:11:41,320
I'm going to summon Huo Minxian's soul

184
00:11:41,320 --> 00:11:43,030
and bring her back
for a ghost wedding with me.

185
00:11:43,030 --> 00:11:44,390
Then we'll get her dowry

186
00:11:44,670 --> 00:11:45,870
of 5 planes, won't we?

187
00:11:48,550 --> 00:11:50,280
Sister, let Mother rest first.

188
00:11:50,390 --> 00:11:51,030
Mother.

189
00:11:52,750 --> 00:11:53,270
Qingyi.

190
00:11:53,550 --> 00:11:54,030
Qingyi!

191
00:11:59,030 --> 00:11:59,870
I believe you

192
00:12:00,390 --> 00:12:01,600
didn't hurt Miss Huo.

193
00:12:02,510 --> 00:12:03,270
I promise you

194
00:12:04,150 --> 00:12:05,790
I will find out the whole truth

195
00:12:05,790 --> 00:12:06,720
of this matter.

196
00:12:10,200 --> 00:12:11,000
Mother...

197
00:12:11,910 --> 00:12:12,910
is just like this,

198
00:12:13,000 --> 00:12:14,000
having a sharp tongue

199
00:12:14,000 --> 00:12:14,930
but a soft heart.

200
00:12:15,390 --> 00:12:17,050
Don't always contradict her.

201
00:12:18,840 --> 00:12:21,570
You really think of yourself
as my older brother,

202
00:12:21,670 --> 00:12:23,470
settling family disputes here?

203
00:12:25,360 --> 00:12:26,670
If you want to play house so much,

204
00:12:26,670 --> 00:12:27,800
go play with Qingyu.

205
00:12:28,000 --> 00:12:29,460
I don't have time for that.

206
00:12:32,200 --> 00:12:33,400
Food is ready at home.

207
00:12:33,720 --> 00:12:34,920
Eat before you leave.

208
00:12:36,320 --> 00:12:37,270
Home?

209
00:12:38,670 --> 00:12:40,550
Are you a Murong or a Li?

210
00:12:40,910 --> 00:12:42,360
Let me give you a piece of advice.

211
00:12:42,360 --> 00:12:43,600
If you try to please both sides,

212
00:12:43,600 --> 00:12:44,930
you'll fail both sides.

213
00:12:45,270 --> 00:12:46,270
Sooner or later, you'll have to figure out

214
00:12:46,270 --> 00:12:47,510
who you really are.

215
00:12:48,550 --> 00:12:49,410
What about you?

216
00:12:53,550 --> 00:12:54,320
Me?

217
00:12:56,790 --> 00:12:59,000
Neither the Li family
nor the Murong family

218
00:12:59,000 --> 00:12:59,960
is my home.

219
00:13:11,000 --> 00:13:12,030
Murong Qingyi's men

220
00:13:12,030 --> 00:13:13,830
are taking Butler Li to the pier.

221
00:13:14,270 --> 00:13:16,930
They probably
want to let him return to Feng'an.

222
00:13:19,360 --> 00:13:20,870
We can't keep Butler Li alive.

223
00:13:20,870 --> 00:13:22,870
Have Yinwei find a chance to strike.

224
00:13:23,270 --> 00:13:24,000
Understood.

225
00:13:24,910 --> 00:13:26,390
But just killing Butler Li

226
00:13:26,600 --> 00:13:28,670
won't eliminate
the future trouble completely.

227
00:13:28,670 --> 00:13:29,400
Don't forget

228
00:13:30,030 --> 00:13:31,560
who brought Butler Li here.

229
00:13:34,960 --> 00:13:36,150
I know what to do.

230
00:13:55,510 --> 00:13:57,310
Young Master Qingyi, I checked.

231
00:13:57,390 --> 00:13:58,510
This person is the servant
in the Huo family who found

232
00:13:58,510 --> 00:14:00,710
clues to Huo Minxian's disappearance.

233
00:14:00,750 --> 00:14:02,350
But why did he meet Miss Fang?

234
00:14:03,120 --> 00:14:05,720
Could this have something to do
with Miss Fang?

235
00:14:09,920 --> 00:14:12,350
[Murong Residence]

236
00:14:25,120 --> 00:14:26,200
You recognized it?

237
00:14:29,320 --> 00:14:31,000
Miss Huo's dress

238
00:14:31,390 --> 00:14:33,240
was designed by a British designer

239
00:14:33,240 --> 00:14:34,790
and made by a French tailor.

240
00:14:35,270 --> 00:14:37,070
Even the fabric is custom-made.

241
00:14:37,550 --> 00:14:39,510
It's the only one in all of Nancheng.

242
00:14:39,510 --> 00:14:41,240
With this amount of blood loss,

243
00:14:41,270 --> 00:14:43,800
it's really hard to say
if she's dead or alive.

244
00:14:44,790 --> 00:14:46,270
What a pity for this dress.

245
00:14:47,080 --> 00:14:48,940
The disappearance of Huo Minxian

246
00:14:49,240 --> 00:14:50,270
was your doing?

247
00:14:52,080 --> 00:14:54,540
If you hadn't brought Butler Li
to Nancheng,

248
00:14:54,720 --> 00:14:56,980
Huo Minxian wouldn't have disappeared.

249
00:14:57,270 --> 00:14:59,080
You caused trouble for me first,

250
00:14:59,440 --> 00:15:00,120
didn't you?

251
00:15:11,630 --> 00:15:13,320
Now everyone thinks

252
00:15:13,600 --> 00:15:15,440
you killed Huo Minxian.

253
00:15:23,480 --> 00:15:24,200
Why?

254
00:15:24,840 --> 00:15:26,030
Why did you do this?

255
00:15:26,550 --> 00:15:29,010
You should have
kept Butler Li in your hands.

256
00:15:29,270 --> 00:15:31,130
Then I would have to listen to you.

257
00:15:32,080 --> 00:15:33,600
But you had to let him go.

258
00:15:34,510 --> 00:15:35,200
Now,

259
00:15:36,120 --> 00:15:37,850
he will never say one more word.

260
00:15:39,960 --> 00:15:41,080
Butler Li—

261
00:15:41,910 --> 00:15:43,000
you killed him too?

262
00:15:44,120 --> 00:15:46,380
He did so many dirty deeds for Huo Mingxi.

263
00:15:46,840 --> 00:15:48,370
He deserved to die long ago.

264
00:15:54,600 --> 00:15:57,320
Don't think everything is fine
just because you killed Butler Li.

265
00:15:57,320 --> 00:15:58,600
I know who you are.

266
00:15:59,000 --> 00:16:01,060
I can go tell the Huo family right now.

267
00:16:01,480 --> 00:16:02,240
Go ahead.

268
00:16:02,240 --> 00:16:04,320
Go tell everyone I'm Ren Susu.

269
00:16:05,030 --> 00:16:07,240
Anyway, today it's a bloody wedding dress.

270
00:16:07,240 --> 00:16:09,040
Tomorrow, it might be her corpse

271
00:16:09,670 --> 00:16:10,670
lying on the bed

272
00:16:10,670 --> 00:16:11,960
in your room.

273
00:16:13,720 --> 00:16:15,380
Tell me, when that time comes,

274
00:16:15,630 --> 00:16:17,430
will the Huo family believe you,

275
00:16:18,150 --> 00:16:20,950
or believe
that you killed Mr. Huo and his daughter

276
00:16:21,030 --> 00:16:23,000
and then framed the eldest daughter
of the Fang family in Nanyang

277
00:16:23,000 --> 00:16:24,630
for the murders?

278
00:16:26,750 --> 00:16:28,030
I'm very curious.

279
00:16:43,270 --> 00:16:45,270
Don't say things you shouldn't say.

280
00:16:45,720 --> 00:16:47,580
Don't do things you shouldn't do.

281
00:16:47,910 --> 00:16:48,870
Murong Qingyi,

282
00:16:50,320 --> 00:16:51,980
if you keep standing in my way,

283
00:16:53,030 --> 00:16:55,160
do you really think I won't fight back?

284
00:16:57,390 --> 00:16:58,550
Ren Susu,

285
00:17:00,240 --> 00:17:01,960
