to what you've told me?

287
00:17:33,350 --> 00:17:36,240
♪ Hate is the smoke left by dying flames ♪

288
00:17:37,360 --> 00:17:39,730
♪ Love is the warmth
lingering after the wildfire ♪

289
00:17:40,890 --> 00:17:43,490
♪ Love and hate collide in a blaze ♪

290
00:17:44,930 --> 00:17:47,650
♪ Devour me all ♪

291
00:17:47,680 --> 00:17:50,600
♪ Ahead lies
a tangle of joys and sorrows ♪

292
00:17:51,850 --> 00:17:53,850
♪ Behind remain
the bitterness of unspoken feelings ♪

293
00:17:54,950 --> 00:17:58,210
♪ The heart races with every thought ♪

294
00:17:58,250 --> 00:18:01,510
♪ As long as we loved each other,
I don't care ♪

295
00:18:01,530 --> 00:18:04,460
♪ If it's a blessing or a curse ♪

296
00:18:06,950 --> 00:18:09,760
♪ This spark of wildfire
spreading across the plains ♪

297
00:18:10,690 --> 00:18:13,360
♪ Stirs embers that refuse to fade ♪

298
00:18:14,350 --> 00:18:18,610
♪ The love that refused to die ♪

299
00:18:21,070 --> 00:18:24,990
♪ Has already consumed us both ♪

300
00:18:30,370 --> 00:18:33,120
[Li Residence]

301
00:18:37,400 --> 00:18:38,030
Father.

302
00:18:39,750 --> 00:18:40,960
